70010000042533.description:
FLATLAND - Vol. 2 is a fast-paced hardcore platformer featuring hand-crafted levels and Lightning-fast respawns. Help Square in crossing the most dangerous part of Flatland: the flooded wells.

Key features:

- Controls are simple and accessible but with several layers of depth to master;
- A lot of itens to collect and new game modes to unlock;
- Lightning-fast respawns keep you in the flow even in more difficult levels;
- Challenging, fast and fun gameplay.

70010000043285.description:
Cats are amazing friends and witness so many special moments in its parents’ lives. They are quiet but watch everything. Secretly support the pursuit of love and happiness. 

In this jigsaw puzzle game, find six of these moments with Buddy the cat.

Features

- Get involved with this love story, with moments of unlikely coincidence, uncertainty and closeness;
- Set up the jigsaw puzzle scenes at five different levels of difficulty;
- Beautiful illustrations created by @Katia.Numakura especially for the game;
- Relax with an immersive and exclusive soundtrack;
